name: Dark Roots 02
description:
“Dark roots” is the result of a creative collaboration with seven performing artists and an intent to recognize a humanity-nature articulation beyond the usual environmentalist formulation: it clearly expresses our complex separation and interdependence with the natural, and indicates a certain pain and anguish in that relationship.

Credits: Pablo Chaco, Colectivo Lóbulo Frontal

Image size: 4900px x 7360px at 300dpi

Dear art lover, if you collect the complete series, please DM me on Twitter (https://twitter.com/Pa3loChaco) to send you a print of your favorite image. 

Vertical size: 30cm x 45cm // Horizontal size: 45cm x 30cm 
(Note that print is not fine art paper. If you would like a fine art paper print, we can arrange it ;)
